tellraw @s ["",{"text":"Getting Spectral Stars","color":"aqua"},"\nSpectral Stars can be acquired in 3 ways:\n\n1. You can craft one Spectral Star using 5 diamonds. The crafting recipe for this is 5 diamonds in a plus (+) shape.\n\n2. Every Minecraft day, players are assigned a new daily quest. Completing this gives you three Spectral Stars. Your daily quest can be found using /trigger daily.\n\n3. In the Advancements menu, you can complete Diamond Spells advancements for Spectral Stars depending on their difficulty. Easy ones give 5, intermediate ones give 10, and hard ones give 20."]